{"tid":586373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"203c九巴司機係又一城附近拒載導盲犬!","createTime":"2018-03-09T12:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T09:51:58.000Z","uid":60219,"like":63,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbe1c32ddfbfef87340fd76fedf6944c6c08d81","tid":586373,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"頭先我大概8:20pm途徑九龍塘生產力促進局巴士站跑緊步<br />\n<br />\n巴士站有個女人拖住隻訓練中黑色導盲犬，截咗架往尖東203c巴士<br />\n<br />\n個司機望咗個女人一眼就直接踩油加速走，勁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我睇唔切個司機咩樣，但睇到個車牌號碼係RG4XXX<br />\n<br />\n即刻開九巴app開file投訴條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n如果你係頭先個女人而你見到呢個post，你可以用編號lca004896既file向九巴跟進<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/204256_24c3d1cfc5c6ac7e6addda71c17e5a33.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F204256_24c3d1cfc5c6ac7e6addda71c17e5a33.png&h=e4b715bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/09/204305_a9c3f7e94c31711fabfcb87919d472c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F204305_a9c3f7e94c31711fabfcb87919d472c0.png&h=b5cb0bf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c0542e70a802c4ced61c10bc0e3a0e3b77c5a43","tid":586373,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"bbd15278436103f23b8101d341df6f6a3a10bef5","tid":586373,"uid":51701,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:44:29.000Z","msg":"岩啦，九巴車長抵投"},{"pid":"bb1e11eb0f3b90f2aa1d60c2f8d182e540dda871","tid":586373,"uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"現階段法例冇話一定要接訓練緊嘅導盲犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同十字冰室嗰單嘢一樣<br />\n不過今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1887d43